[{"title":"Linux下轻量级启动器Albert","url":"http://51simple.com/linux-lightweight-launcher-albert.html","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>Access everything with virtually zero effort. Run applications, open files or their paths, open bookmarks in your browser, search the web, calculate things and a lot more</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ManuelSchneid3r/albert/master/v0.8.11.gif\" alt=\"albert\"></p>\n<p>Ubuntu下安装Albert:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo add-apt-repository ppa:nilarimogard/webupd8</div><div class=\"line\">sudo apt-get update</div><div class=\"line\">sudo apt-get install albert</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>若使用fcitx输入法，无法输入中文搜索，请执行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo apt install fcitx-frontend-qt5</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><a href=\"https://albertlauncher.github.io/docs/installing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">更多详情</a></p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["Albert"]},{"title":"ssh免密码登陆vps服务器","url":"http://51simple.com/ssh-login-server-no-password.html","content":"<blockquote>\n<p>vps服务器操作系统是Centos7，我的电脑是Linux Mint，实现原理是通过密钥文件免认证。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>1、首先用 <code>ssh-keygen</code> 生成密钥，客户端和服务器都得执行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">ssh-keygen -t rsa -P &apos;&apos;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>完成之后，在 <code>~/.ssh</code> 目录下会生成两个文件，id_rsa(私钥)与id_rsa.pub(公钥)。</p>\n<p>2、接下来，把客户端的公钥文件上传到服务器中：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">scp .ssh/id_rsa.pub username@host:.ssh/authorized_keys</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>其中的 <code>username</code> 是服务器用户名，<code>host</code> 是服务器ip地址。</p>\n<p>3、最后重启服务器的 <code>sshd</code> 服务即可：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">systemctl restart sshd</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["ssh","vps"]},{"title":"解决eclipse中logcat只显示级别","url":"http://51simple.com/eclipse-logcat-show-level-only.html","content":"<p><img src=\"http://7xl7v5.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/eclipse-logcat-show-level-only.jpg\" alt=\"eclipse-logcat-show-level-only\"></p>\n<p>在 <code>linux</code> 下才会出现的问题，解决方法如下：</p>\n<p>1、关闭eclipse</p>\n<p>2、在终端执行:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">sudo nano ~/workspace/.metadata/.plugins/org.eclipse.core.runtime/.settings/com.android.ide.eclipse.ddms.prefs</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3、用以下文本替换原有内容</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">ddms.logcat.automonitor.userprompt=true  </div><div class=\"line\">eclipse.preferences.version=1</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Application=169</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Level=54</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.PID=54</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Tag=198</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Text=619</div><div class=\"line\">logcat.view.colsize.Time=182</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>4、重新打开eclipse，logcat就能正常显示了。</p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["eclipse"]},{"title":"Win10去除桌面快捷方式小箭头","url":"http://51simple.com/win10-remove-shoutcut-arrow.html","content":"<p>在桌面新建一个文本文档，重命名为 <code>clearArrow.bat</code>，再编辑写入以下内容：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">reg add &quot;HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Explorer\\Shell Icons&quot; /v 29 /d &quot;%systemroot%\\system32\\imageres.dll,197&quot; /t reg_sz /f</div><div class=\"line\">taskkill /f /im explorer.exe</div><div class=\"line\">attrib -s -r -h &quot;%userprofile%\\AppData\\Local\\iconcache.db&quot;</div><div class=\"line\">del &quot;%userprofile%\\AppData\\Local\\iconcache.db&quot; /f /q</div><div class=\"line\">start explorer</div><div class=\"line\">pause</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>保存之后，选中文件并右键，选择 <code>以管理员身份运行</code>，这样快捷方式小箭头便清除了。</p>\n<p>附件：<a href=\"https://pan.baidu.com/s/1ge2NkQJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">clearArrow.bat</a></p>\n","categories":["Windows"],"tags":["快捷方式"]},{"title":"PotPlayer 免安装绿色版","url":"http://51simple.com/potplayer-green-version.html","content":"<p><img src=\"http://7xl7v5.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/potplayer-cut.jpg\" alt=\"potplayer\"></p>\n<p>PotPlayer是 Windows 下非常优秀的一款音视频播放器，支持大多数的文件格式。官网只有安装版，这里提供免安装的版本，点此下载</p>\n<p>下载之后，解压出一个 <code>PotPlayer</code> 文件夹，里面有个 <code>PotPlayerMini.exe</code>，选中它并右键，选择<code>发送到</code> -&gt;     <code>桌面快捷方式</code>。</p>\n","categories":["Windows"],"tags":["免安装"]},{"title":"Linux去除烦人的sudo密码","url":"http://51simple.com/linux-remove-sudo-password.html","content":"<p>执行 sudo 命令需要频繁输入密码，虽说更安全，但也挺烦人的，我选择去除它。</p>\n<p>打开终端，执行 <code>sudo visudo</code>，找到这一行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">%sudo  ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在行首添加 <code>#</code>，即注释掉此行，再往下添加一行：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\">%sudo ALL=NOPASSWD:ALL</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>保存修改之后，以后执行 sudo 命令就畅通无阻了。</p>\n","categories":["Linux"],"tags":["sudo密码"]},{"title":"BaiduPCS - 百度网盘命令行工具","url":"http://51simple.com/baidupcs.html","content":"<p>BaiduPCS 是一个多线程下载或上传百度网盘的命令行工具，可以在 linux终端 中使用。当然也支持Windows, Mac平台，关键在于<code>不限速</code>。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>简单介绍一下windows下的使用方法：</p>\n<p>1、下载 <a href=\"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1miFe1r6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">pcs.exe</a>，并移到到个人用户目录下（如 C:\\用户\\Simple）<br>2、按Win+r快捷键，输入cmd回车，即可打开命令窗口<br>3、执行 <code>pcs set --max_thread=3</code>设置最大下载线程数<br>4、执行 <code>pcs login --username=gang --password=&quot;password&quot;</code> ，对应自己的帐号密码进行登陆<br>5、之后就是一些操作文件的命令，详情见作者<a href=\"https://github.com/GangZhuo/BaiduPCS/blob/master/README.md#命令列表&quot;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">github主页</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>提示：把 pcs.exe 所在目录加入到系统的环境变量（Path）中会更方便，这样不管当前目录是什么，都能使用 pcs 命令。</p>\n</blockquote>\n","categories":["Tutorial"],"tags":["百度云不限速"]},{"title":"about","url":"http://51simple.com/about/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"category","url":"http://51simple.com/category/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"","url":"http://51simple.com/css/custom.css","content":"@font-face {\n  font-family: \"Meiryo\";\n  src: url(\"/fonts/Meiryo.eot\");\n  /* IE9 */\n  src: url(\"/fonts/Meiryo.eot?#iefix\") format(\"embedded-opentype\"), /* IE6-IE8 */\n  url(\"/fonts/Meiryo.woff\") format(\"woff\"), /* chrome, firefox */\n  url(\"/fonts/Meiryo.ttf\") format(\"truetype\"), /* chrome, firefox, opera, Safari, Android, iOS 4.2+ */\n  url(\"/fonts/Meiryo.svg#Meiryo\") format(\"svg\");\n  /* iOS 4.1- */\n  font-style: normal;\n  font-weight: normal;\n}\n\n.article-content p {\n  letter-spacing: 1px;\n  font-size: 16px;\n  color: #444\n}\n\n.content.content-post .article-header .article-meta {\n  font-size: 13px\n}\n\n.highlight pre {\n  font-family: Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,\"Courier New\",monospace;\n}\n\ncode {\n  font-family: Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,\"Courier New\",monospace;\n}\n\ncode:lang(zh){\nfont-family: monospace, sans-serif;\n}\n","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"link","url":"http://51simple.com/link/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"project","url":"http://51simple.com/project/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"search","url":"http://51simple.com/search/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]},{"title":"tag","url":"http://51simple.com/tag/index.html","content":"","categories":[],"tags":[]}]